kohlberg  company closes on  billion kohlberg investors viii  business wire kohlberg  company closes on  billion kohlberg investors viii december    am eastern standard time mt kisco nybusiness wirekohlberg  company llc “kohlberg” a private equity firm specializing in middle market investing announced today the final closing of its eighth private equity fund kohlberg investors viii lp with  billion in total commitments the fund was oversubscribed and closed at its “hard cap” due to strong support from existing limited partners coupled with commitments from new leading institutional investors “we are deeply gratified by the tremendous support from our existing limited partner base and pleased to welcome several new distinguished limited partners to fund viii” said sam frieder managing partner at kohlberg “our success in raising the fund is continued validation of our investment philosophy and the strength and quality of our team” over  investors participated as limited partners in kohlberg investors viii including a broad mix of public and corporate pension funds endowments insurance companies and family offices across the globe lazard acted as placement agent for kohlberg while ropes  gray served as legal counsel in the formation of kohlberg investors viii about kohlberg  company llc kohlberg  company llc is a private equity firm specializing in middle market investing since its inception in  kohlberg has organized eight private equity funds through which it has raised  billion of committed equity capital the firm has completed  controlbuyout transactions and over  addon acquisitions with an aggregate transaction value of over  billion kohlberg invests across five industry segments industrial manufacturing consumer products business services healthcare services and financial services the firm concentrates on transactions with ebitda between  million and  million where it can invest between  million and  million of equity for more information please visit wwwkohlberg